example.code:
PS C:\>Get-IAMAttachedGroupPolicyList -GroupName "Admins"
PolicyArn PolicyName --------- ---------- arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/SecurityAudit SecurityAudit arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/AdministratorAccess AdministratorAccess
example.description: This command returns the names and ARNs of the managed policies that are attached to the IAM group named Admins in the AWS account. To see the list of inline policies embedded in the group, use the Get-IAMGroupPolicyList command.
